{"tid":295644,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)美國眾神","createTime":"2017-06-24T02:35:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-24T17:26:03.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"53a8e8321282fb9171d72e74c21fcc36757f723b","tid":295644,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T02:35:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">播唔曬下次播返</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=V%2FzvkibrovXKhrUX6s6g757TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=d0a09272\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> CC台又執柒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=V%2FzvkibrovXKhrUX6s6g757TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=469fdfeb\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a>可以直接睇到V台<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=V%2FzvkibrovXKhrUX6s6g757TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=2ba4c476\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.nuxbox.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/ian-mcshane-american-gods-serie-2017.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nuxbox.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F01%2Fian-mcshane-american-gods-serie-2017.jpg&h=c63b5b05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dramaqueen.com.tw/features/20170509/001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dramaqueen.com.tw%2Ffeatures%2F20170509%2F001.html&d=V%2FzvkibrovXKhrUX6s6g757TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=b42c2b75\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dramaqueen.com.tw/features/20170509/001.html</a> &lt;角色介紹<br />\n原著小說於2001年出版，先後被翻譯成30多種語言，在全球廣為流傳。故事描述一場即將到來的戰爭，對立的雙方是聖經故事和神話傳說中的「古代眾神」和代表新世界的「美國眾神」。<br />\n<br />\n該劇描述在監牢中的男主角─影，等待著有天可以出獄，望向藍天，重回妻子、好友的懷抱。某天，一條消息到來，他可以提前兩天出獄，但卻是因為他的愛妻和好友同時車禍身亡，出獄後的他失去了一切，除了自由。從監獄釋放後，穿越美國大陸的旅行過程中的一系列奇遇。講述了他與生活在美國土地上的各種神祇相遇，由此引發了出許多精彩動人、奇詭絢麗的故事"},{"pid":"6a63f1678eaa4f70d74f67f7cf61d52f37cbf408","tid":295644,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T02:40:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c11bfbe2902d69cc7440bef5990b090ad0bb871c","tid":295644,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T03:10:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f595328d037f8ab67b5568c4e280fe401a193148","tid":295644,"uid":78392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T03:11:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"706852504d4866a84802e399274fc4b7b6a77a30","tid":295644,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T03:40:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"087ee70f4f13416468b7f083c59bfb4705a090a1","tid":295644,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T04:36:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27837e23eff0cdf3f58d780a0f8e88eee6609f00","tid":295644,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-2